verbose_text: The expression of ATOH7, a key gene that regulates the fate of RGCs, was significantly high in the 10-day gene transfected groups (DLNAD-10d : 236; DLNAD-Neural-10d : 694-fold change) (XREF_FIG), and high in the 20-day transfected and non transfected groups, albeit with no statistical significance (XREF_FIG).
